OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry today with plenty of
OL,6,Fsunshine at first. A veil of high
OL,7,Fcloud will move across for a time,
OL,8,Fturning the sunshine hazy, but it will
OL,9,Fstill feel warm in the light winds,
OL,10,Fand clearer weather will return later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FStaying dry tonight with
OL,13,Fclear skies for a while, though some
OL,14,Fcloud arriving from the east.
OL,15,FTemperatures will fall under the clear
OL,16,Fspells to give a patchy rural frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
