OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,6,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,7,FBright at first, but skies turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy with a small chance
OL,9,Fof the odd shower.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FA few
OL,12,Fshowers possible on Monday, otherwise
OL,13,Fit looks dry with some warm sunny
OL,14,Fspells at times. Turning a little
OL,15,Fbreezy on Wednesday. Some chilly
OL,16,Fnights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
